data.description: 3 bedroom 2 Bathroom for lease in Hollywood/Scotsman! Granite countertops in Kitchen, Vaulted Living Room Ceilings and very clean home! Easy access to Bell St and Western St. Short-term lease possible 3-12 months. Landlord says would consider paying utilities based on lease duration. Bonus workspace/office/bedroom in garage. Has a concrete pad in backyard and storage shed. Washer and Dryer stay no refrigerator. Carpets were cleaned 1/15/2021. Pets a possibility with deposit per pet and no aggressive breeds. Go and Show!
